BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313847943@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260322T032028Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20260327T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20260327T190000
SUMMARY:Bourbon Friday // Networking & Bourbon Tasting
DESCRIPTION:Bourbon Friday\nJoin us at Techartista Central West End on Fri
 day\, March 27th\, for Bourbon Friday\, a weekly social gathering celebrat
 ing the St. Louis startup scene. Each week\, we come together to share our
  stories\, struggles\, experiences\, and\, yes\, a little bit of bourbon.\
 n\n**Mingle & Tastings // 4-7pm**\n\n**Parking & Transportation**\nStreet 
 parking is available for Bourbon Friday.\nYou may also park in the church 
 parking lot across the street from TechArtista.\nWe are also only a 1-mile
  Walk from [Central West End Metro Station](https://www.metrostlouis.org/m
 etrolink-station/central-west-end-station/).\n\n**========================
 ========**\n\n**18+ to attend without a parent or legal guardian.**\n**21+
  and up to drink ... obviously.**\n**Please Drink Responsibly.**\n\n*Under
 age drinking will result in removal from the event and a permanent ban fro
 m all future events.*
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/bourbonfridays/events/313847943/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260319T065215Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260319T065215Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
